3. **Added static scheduling to orders scan** (was: 178.73ms)
   - Changed from default dynamic scheduling to `schedule(static, 10000)` morsel size
   - This reduces scheduling overhead and improves cache locality
   - Expected improvement: ~5-10% on orders scan phase

